title_bed_bats_review: Boutique hotel in Gaibandha District · 1 bedroom · 1 bed · 1 private bath
listing_description: Enjoy the glamour of this stylish, upscale place in Gaibandha. SKS Inn is the largest multi-cuisine 4-Star Resort in North Bengal, Bangladesh. Upgraded rooms include Lake views, minibars, and access to a Restaurant with complimentary breakfast and all-day refreshments. Suites add living rooms and kitchens. There's a refined international restaurant and a brasserie serving afternoon tea, as well as a Cafe. Amenities include a fitness room, meeting rooms, banquet and parking.

title_bed_bats_review: Rental unit in Sirajganj · 2 bedrooms · 2 beds · 2 baths
listing_description: Relax with the whole family at this peaceful place to stay.Welcome to our cozy 1st-floor apartment near Ullapara Rail Station! With 2 beds, 2 baths (including an attached one), dining & drawing areas, and a fully-equipped kitchen, it's perfect for a relaxing stay. Bed linen provided. Explore nearby attractions like Chalan Beel, Hazrat Shah Kamal Shrine, Taat Shilpo Village & enjoy local various foods and delicacies. Experience comfort and convenience in the heart of Ullapara, Sirajganj.
